<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>홈 - 홀로서기 심리학</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@300;400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <header class="header">
        <div class="container">
            <nav class="nav">
                <a href="/" class="logo">홀로서기 심리학</a>
                <ul class="nav-list">
                    <li><a href="/">홈</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/chapters">목차</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/about">책 소개</a></li>
                </ul>
            </nav>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main class="main">
        <div class="hero-section">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1 class="hero-title"><%= book.title %></h1>
            <h2 class="hero-subtitle"><%= book.subtitle %></h2>
            <p class="hero-description"><%= book.description %></p>
            <div class="hero-actions">
                <a href="/chapters" class="btn btn-primary">📚 목차 보기<span class="btn-icon">✨</span></a>
                <a href="/about" class="btn btn-secondary">🌟 책 소개<span class="btn-icon">🎯</span></a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-image">
            <div class="book-mockup">
                <div class="book-cover">
                    <h3>🌟 홀로서기<br>심리학 ✨</h3>
                    <p>🌱 진정한 나를 찾아가는<br>심리적 독립의 여정 🦋</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<section class="featured-chapters">
    <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">📖 주요 챕터 ✨</h2>
        <div class="chapters-grid">
            <% book.chapters.slice(0, 3).forEach(chapter => { %>
            <div class="chapter-card">
                <div class="chapter-number">Chapter <%= chapter.id %></div>
                <h3 class="chapter-title"><%= chapter.title %></h3>
                <p class="chapter-subtitle"><%= chapter.subtitle %></p>
                <p class="chapter-summary"><%= chapter.summary %></p>
                <a href="/chapter/<%= chapter.id %>" class="chapter-link">🔍 자세히 보기 <span class="btn-icon">✨</span></a>
            </div>
            <% }); %>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="book-benefits">
    <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">🌟 이 책을 읽고 나면 🎯</h2>
        <div class="benefits-grid">
            <% book.benefits.forEach((benefit, index) => { %>
            <div class="benefit-item">
                <div class="benefit-icon"><%= ['🌟', '💎', '🎯', '🚀', '💝'][index % 5] %></div>
                <p><%= benefit %></p>
            </div>
            <% }); %>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="target-audience">
    <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">💝 이런 분들께 추천합니다 🎪</h2>
        <div class="audience-grid">
            <% book.targetAudience.forEach((audience, index) => { %>
            <div class="audience-item">
                <div class="audience-icon"><%= ['👥', '💼', '🎓', '❤️', '🌱'][index % 5] %></div>
                <p><%= audience %></p>
            </div>
            <% }); %>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="cta-section">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="cta-content">
            <h2>🌈 심리적 독립의 여정을 시작하세요 ✨</h2>
            <p>🦋 진정한 나를 찾아가는 마법같은 여행에 지금 동참하세요 🌟</p>
            <a href="/chapters" class="btn btn-primary btn-large">📚 목차 살펴보기<span class="btn-icon">🚀</span></a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
    </main>

    <footer class="footer">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="footer-content">
                <div class="footer-section">
                    <h3>홀로서기 심리학</h3>
                    <p>진정한 나를 찾아가는 심리적 독립의 여정</p>
                </div>
                <div class="footer-section">
                    <h4>목차</h4>
                    <ul class="footer-links">
                        <li><a href="/chapters">전체 목차</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/chapter/1">1장. 의존의 뿌리를 파헤치다</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/chapter/5">5장. 스스로 결정하는 용기</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/chapter/10">10장. 성숙한 관계로의 여정</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="footer-section">
                    <h4>연락처</h4>
                    <p>이메일: jihajoung5001@gmail.com</p>
                    <p>GitHub: <a href="https://github.com/jiha-j">jiha-j</a></p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="footer-bottom">
                <p>&copy; 2024 홀로서기 심리학. All rights reserved.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script src="/js/script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>